The flat profile of the wheel in combination with depressed center allows for a wide range of grinding angles (0-45). These 1/4 inch grinding wheels are ideal for heavy stock removal, scale removal, weld removal, weld blending, edge beveling, and torch-cut softening with a right angle grinder. A smaller hub on 4.5 inch wheels keeps the wheel from gouging valuable parts as well as allowing for 30% more usable wheel area.
